"Koga god da zamolite za pomoc, on ce vam dati sve sto ima." *Koga* (Whoever you ask for help, they will give you all they have.) 

"Kad god da se vratim doma, *koga* god da susretnem, svi me pozdravljaju." (Whenever I come home, whoever I meet, they all greet me.) 

"Mislio je da treba da se izvinjava *koga* god da je povredio." (He thought he should apologize to whoever he offended.) 

"Ona je spremna da prisustvuje bilo *kom* dogadjaju." (She is ready to attend any event.) 

"On je obecao da ce biti tu *koga* god da nam zatreba." (He promised to be there whoever we may need.) 

"Koga god da pogledas, svi su zauzeti." (Whoever you look at, they are all busy.)